  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And when the men of Ai looked behind them,.... On some account or another, perhaps observing that the army of Israel made a full stop and was gazing at the city: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "they saw, and, behold, the smoke of the city ascended up to heaven; from whence they concluded an enemy was there, and had set fire to it: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and they had no power to flee this way or that way; for if they turned back to their city there was an enemy, how powerful they knew not, possessed of it, and whom they might expect would meet them; and if they pushed forward, there was the whole army of Israel against them, which now turned and faced them, showing no fear of them: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and the people that fled to the wilderness turned back upon the pursuers; the people of Israel, that fled by the way of the wilderness, Joshua 8:15, turned about, and fell upon the men of Ai that pursued them. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and the people that fled to the wilderness turned back upon the pursuers; the people of Israel, that fled by the way of the wilderness, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:15",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ", turned about, and fell upon the men of Ai that pursued them. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
